<b>MECHANICS:</b>
<ol>
    <li>If member is not yet a GoodKredit subscriber:</li>
    <ol class="small-alpha float-x">
        <li class="float">Download <b>GoodKredit Philippines</b> in Google Play Store.</li>
        <li class="float">Click on ‘Not yet a member?Sign up’.</li>
        <li class="float">Provide the necessary information then click START.</li>
    </ol>
    <li>If member is already a GoodKredit subscriber:</li>
    <ol class="small-alpha float-y">
        <li class="float">Open the GK app.</li>
    </ol>
    <li>Tap <b>CPMPC</b> icon. Then click <b>P2S PLAY TO SAVE</b>.</li>
    <li>Scroll down to <b>Play the Game</b>.</li>
    <li>Select the game that you want to play.</li>
    <ul>
        <li>Click <b>Play Three (3) Digits</b> and fill in the 3 circles with your combination
            numbers, between <b>0-9</b>.
        </li>
        <li>Click <b>Play Six (6) Digits</b> and fill in the 6 circles with your combination
            numbers, between <b>1-46</b>.
        </li>
    </ul>
    <li>Enter the required information to continue.</li>
    <li>Drag vouchers to cover the amount needed to pay. Click <b>PROCEED</b>.</li>
    <li>Check and verify the information and payment details. Click <b>CONFIRM</b>.</li>
    <li>Wait for the confirmation of successful transaction.</li>
    <li>Cut-off time of the game is 3:00 pm and will resume at 6:00 pm. Raffle draw is scheduled every
        4:00-4:30pm, except weekends and holidays.
    </li>
</ol>

<b>DRAW:</b>
<ol>
    <li>The draw will be held every 4:00-4:30pm of CPMPC working day at the head office (may be
        aired in all branches through internet technology).
    </li>
    <li>The draw uses a raffle machine that jumbles numbered "ping-pong" balls inside a transparent
        draw machine. A commission-appointed representative will facilitate the draw.
    </li>
    <li>On or before 6:00 pm, draw must be completed and results will be presented to all members
        via official website, <a href="http://www.mycoop.ph/">www.mycoop.ph</a>, and CPMPC mini app in the
        GoodKredit app.
    </li>
</ol>

</html>